# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# EXIT INTERVIEW → KNOWLEDGE GRAPH  —  Environment Configuration
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
# SETUP INSTRUCTIONS
# ──────────────────
# 1. Copy this file and rename the copy to  .env
#       cp .env.example .env          (Mac / Linux)
#       copy .env.example .env        (Windows)
#
# 2. Fill in the values marked  ← REQUIRED
#
# 3. Never commit .env — it is gitignored. This file (.env.example) is safe
#    to commit because it contains no real secrets.
#
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════


# ── Anthropic API  (REQUIRED) ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
# Get your key at: https://console.anthropic.com/settings/keys
# The free tier is enough to run the golden eval scripts.
#
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=                                  # ← REQUIRED


# ── Model selection  (optional) ───────────────────────────────────────────────
#
# All five specialist agents use this model.  Defaults to Haiku if not set.
#
# Haiku   — fast, cheap, good enough for most extraction tasks (default)
# Sonnet  — higher quality, ~5x cost, recommended for final eval runs
#
# ANTHROPIC_MODEL=claude-haiku-4-5-20251001
# ANTHROPIC_MODEL=claude-sonnet-4-6


# ── FastAPI server  (optional, Phase 7+) ──────────────────────────────────────
#
# Only needed once the live WebSocket interface is built.
# Leave commented out for now.
#
# APP_HOST=127.0.0.1
# APP_PORT=8000
